Freddie Gray died from spinal injuries on April 19 after he was arrested on April 12  . 
  A wake was held for Gray on Sunday in Baltimore and his funeral will be held on Monday . 
  Gray was arrested for carrying a knife but died a week after the incident from a severed spine . 
  Earlier in the day, a pastor at Gray's family church said 'somebody is going to have to pay' for his death . 
 